reviewText: Niece is 2 - perhaps too young for this one
My Son loves Octonauts. This is best way to watch them when we don't have internet.
Great video for my just three granddaughter.  She is totally into Octonauts (and Disney primcesses.).  This one was priced right.
My 20 month old son loves this DVD!
They love watching this DVD.  Really great for any who love the Octonauts!
